Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到寒空中有不耳熟的悲傷的聲音在回蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的…聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鎮子裡的病到底是從何時開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在十四年前就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家看起來沒什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但皮膚各處變得非常堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腳也變得不靈活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情最嚴重的人  是我的老友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連起床也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位患者在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮西頭那家的夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的人都說  他們的女兒是病因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩叫茂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那女孩出生以來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人相繼得病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的確也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四年間雖竭盡所能  但仍找不出原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那女孩緊閉嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家只是心存懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  來  這個月的份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為和你的父母雙親是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其同情這樣的孩子還不如給我們加點工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  有個大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  沒有替換的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣  這個鎮子的人都不厭煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪怕說句話也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的傳聞是假話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不會希望自己的家人和朋友得病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的村子也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兩年前的暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人和朋友都只剩下一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定代替父親在這裡一直拼命勞動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是不得不決定這樣做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打聽一下那個女孩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是被老爺請來的醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道喲  因為她一句話也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵  做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…回來…啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是茂…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得見這種「鏽」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫銀古
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被請來治病的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會責問你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種病能醫治的  我只是來和你說幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的話即使出聲也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想生銹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…也看得見鏽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種聲音很可怕  所以我想毀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與她短小身材不相稱的  粗糙嘶啞的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個洞裡  把嗓子喊成了這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻帶有甜澀餘音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論怎麼改變嗓音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲音依然會產生銹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著不可思議回音的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個娃娃怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一出聲  周圍的人身上和物體上就產生銹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也以為那是很正常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  茂  唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不帶任何疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家唱了我喜歡的歌聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大家看不到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發覺到這是件壞事時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從大家感到身體不靈活開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我四歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那件事告訴了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂  這事對任何人都絕不可以說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說了的話  就不能再待在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經  不能再工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能活下去  也是多虧了宅院老爺的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依賴現在在這裡欺騙大家的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到遲早能夠償還的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不要出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以後我就沒有向任何人開過口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和人說話是十年以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招到大家的討厭也是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我選擇了使一家三口保住性命的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是越聽越奇異的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能發出這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是混合了人不能發出的層次的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能你自己聽起來似乎是有些不同的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我身邊就有酷似你的聲音的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是鏽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫「野鏽」的有生命的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的看得見  有的看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是具有不同的應有狀態的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野鏽是通常附著在生物的屍骸上  以對其進行分解的無害的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候就會發出某種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音就像是放大了數百倍的這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為判斷有食物  山裡的野鏽就集中過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒有吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此連活著的東西都附上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真如此  把它們驅散的話就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:11:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  應該有恢復「你的聲音」的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼上都附著啊  沒有喜惡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部一視同仁地染上了鏽色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼寒冷的地方  做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你不害怕茂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我來這個鎮子還不到兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以並沒有茂是病因的體會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為連一個野鏽也沒附著的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如  醫治好大家的病  我也能出聲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能向鐵道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用自己的聲音說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  為了除掉蟲子要利用你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  那之後必須離開這個鎮子才能安全過活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病能醫治吧  不管讓我做什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想請你教我寫字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手巾？謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  知道原因了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  茂是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那只是謠傳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我唸給你聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和你說話的話  你也會得病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在一直很抱歉  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵  這是誰寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是茂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不還  也只有你會同情她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個給老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼呢  鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別追了  快把信從灶裡取出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不能讓她用「不知道」蒙混過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到別處去吧  茂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家馬上就要來了  也不知他們要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒跟銀古先生學除掉蟲的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在暫且先離開這裡  到那座山嶺上等著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會說服大家  然後在那裡教你除掉蟲的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經不能再待在這個鎮子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山嶺和我的村子是同一個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人太危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吧  茂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀古先生  為什麼袒護茂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓茂出來  讓她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使驅逐茂也治不好病  這不是茂的過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂只是像普通孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話  笑  唱歌  僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那「聲音」裡有使成為病因的東西聚集的要素而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個與我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是她該怎樣向得病的人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉的話  十年間茂應該一直在做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打破禁忌  說些三言兩語的推託之辭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不會激起大家的懷疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪的話  她早就背負了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能因此而原諒她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的孩子跟那孩子同齡卻不能走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  你們會得到補償
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果招致病的是茂的聲音  能消除的也是那種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們不能把它變成尾帳合在一起算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽涉到這種病的人  大家都一樣痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂  那個信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總使我覺得有你要離開鎮子的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是治好病的話  你要那樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目的地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你也來我的村子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是房子和船大部分都被沖走了的漁村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家正在一點一點地慢慢重建
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的  就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來  出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種距離叫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種病能醫治
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂  鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯聽的那個聲音  在群山間回蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像腿變輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂  沒事吧  鐵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起  連鐵也得病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  這傢伙沒得病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  你那時做了與我想讓你做的相近的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使聲音在圍繞著這鎮子的群山間回蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把聚集在鎮上的野鏽都驅散到山裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  能做到這點的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須是背對著海的那座山嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為野鏽討厭「潮氣」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在刮進海風的鎮子邊緣的地方附著的鏽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是野鏽  是普通的鏽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵沒有得病是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在漁村長大的  來這以後也常常吹海風的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也到海邊去的話  就能正常地生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  被驅散的蟲還只是很小的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來只有反覆多年才能全部消除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能  在那之前你的聲音就真的毀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那樣  也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有一點  但我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏽還沒有完全充斥鎮子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我  很喜歡這個鎮子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一點也好  只要能逐漸恢復原來的樣子就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說女孩離開鎮子之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病就慢慢消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山嶺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但據說直到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍能聽見已經毀損但又美妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在群山間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱約回蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}「篝野行」


